# QuantyBT ğŸª

**A lightweight extension for [`vectorbt`](https://github.com/polakowo/vectorbt) focused on statistical robustness, modularity, and seamless strategy integration.**

QuantyBT combines the familiar VectorBT API for fast inâ€‘sample backtests with a suite of builtâ€‘in, advanced validation techniques. Define your strategy exactly as beforeâ€”implementing `preprocess_data`, `generate_signals`, and `param_space`â€”and then unlock:

- **Outâ€‘ofâ€‘Sample Splits** for rigorous train/test separation  
- **Walkâ€‘Forward Optimization** to guard against lookâ€‘ahead bias  
- **Monte Carlo Simulations** for probabilistic performance envelopes  
- **Parameter Sensitivity Analyses** to pinpoint robust hyperparameter regions  

All features plug seamlessly into your existing VectorBT workflows, helping you minimize overfitting and boost the realâ€‘world robustness of your trading algorithmsâ€”without rewriting a single line of strategy code.

