## ğŸš€ Features

- Clean `Strategy` base class for building reusable strategies  
- `Analyzer` with detailed performance metrics (Sharpe, Sortino, Calmar, volatility, drawdown, etc.)  
- Timeâ€‘based train/test split with purge window  
- Builtâ€‘in `hyperopt` integration for parameter optimization  
- Modular structureâ€”easy to extend, simple to use  

